---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy" description="Privacy practices for the DRAGGON Lab website.">
  <section class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: July 2026.</p>
    <p>We do not use advertising trackers, sell personal data, or use analytics for personal profiling. The site uses privacy-friendly aggregate analytics to understand which pages and resources are useful.</p>
    <p>We may count aggregate outbound clicks to selected external resources, such as GitHub repositories, YouTube teaching materials, publication links, and Join / Collaborate contact links. These events help us understand which resources are useful, but they are collected in aggregate and are not used for personal profiling.</p>
    <p>This site does not use analytics cookies. Some external platforms linked from this site may use cookies or similar technologies under their own policies.</p>
    <p>For questions about this site or its privacy practices, contact DRAGGON Lab at <a href="mailto:contact@draggonlab.org">contact@draggonlab.org</a>.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
